<details class="govuk-details">
  <summary class="govuk-details__summary">
    <span class="govuk-details__summary-text">
      What are additional codes?
    </span>
  </summary>
  <div class="govuk-details__text">
    <p class="govuk-body">
    Additional codes are used on the tariff for a number of purposes. The first character of the additional code determines the type of activity it is intended to influence.
    </p>
    <table class="govuk-table">
      <thead class="govuk-table__head">
        <tr class="govuk-table__row">
          <th scope="col" class="govuk-table__header">First character</th>
          <th scope="col" class="govuk-table__header">Meaning</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody class="govuk-table__body">
        <tr class="govuk-table__row">
          <td class="govuk-table__cell">2</td>
          <td class="govuk-table__cell">These codes influence duties, providing preferential tariff treatment under certain circumstances</td>
        </tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row">
          <td class="govuk-table__cell">3</td>
          <td class="govuk-table__cell">These codes impact whether or not a prohibition is to be applied</td>
        </tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row">
          <td class="govuk-table__cell">4</td>
          <td class="govuk-table__cell">These codes impact whether or not a restrictive measure is to be applied</td>
        </tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row">
          <td class="govuk-table__cell">8, A, B or C</td>
          <td class="govuk-table__cell">These codes relate to exporting company for determining applicable anti-dumping or anti-subsidy duty.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row">
          <td class="govuk-table__cell">V</td>
          <td class="govuk-table__cell">These codes impact which VAT rate is due</td>
        </tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row">
          <td class="govuk-table__cell">X</td>
          <td class="govuk-table__cell">These codes impact which excise rate is due</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>
</details>
